== 拍摄与制作 ==
[[File:Qingyan_Town.jpg|thumb]]
电影剧本的蓝本小说《寻枪记》由作家凡一平创作，发表于1999年《[[十月_(杂志)|十月]]》第4期，导演陆川以一万元的低价买下小说的电影改编权。经过两年时间剧本几易其稿，在获得投资方[[华谊兄弟|华谊兄弟]]的认可和监制兼主演姜文的加盟之后，于2001年5月10日开机拍摄<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-cn | publisher = 中国青年 | title = 陆川：我的寻枪记 | url = http://ent.ifeng.com/feichangdao/200904/0423_5223_1123087_1.shtml | author =  | date =  | accessdate = 2010-07-14 | archive-date = 2019-05-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190519150111/http://ent.ifeng.com/feichangdao/200904/0423_5223_1123087_1.shtml | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | language = zh-cn | publisher = 华商报 | title = 《寻枪》背后的故事：《寻枪记》为姜文度身定作 | url = http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/c/2002-06-19/87884.html | author =  | date =  | accessdate = 2010-07-14 | archive-date = 2019-05-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190519173611/http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/c/2002-06-19/87884.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | language = zh-cn | publisher = 北方网 | title = 姜文宁静携手《寻枪》 | url = http://ent.enorth.com.cn/system/2001/04/26/000083860.shtml | author =  | date =  | accessdate = 2010-07-14 | archive-date = 2019-05-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190521035214/http://ent.enorth.com.cn/system/2001/04/26/000083860.shtml | dead-url = no }}</ref>。电影最初选择在[[广西|广西]][[昭平县|昭平县]][[黄姚镇|黄姚镇]]取景，但后来因贵州省大力邀请，影片最终定在贵州省[[贵阳市|贵阳市]][[青岩镇|青岩镇]]拍摄<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-cn | publisher = 光明网 | title = 从《寻枪记》到《寻枪！》 | url = http://www.gmw.cn/content/2006-06/20/content_436850.htm | author = 凡一平 | date =  | accessdate = 2010-07-14 | archive-date = 2013-06-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130602165909/http://www.gmw.cn/content/2006-06/20/content_436850.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。《寻枪》是中国首部运用GDC([[环球数码|环球数码]])旗下的[[DSR|DSR]]数码影院服务系统的胶片数码版电影。<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-cn | publisher = 中国网 | title = 中国数码电影放映　从《寻枪》开始 | url = http://www.china.com.cn/culture/txt/2002-05/08/content_5142440.htm| author =   | date =2002-05-08  | accessdate = 2020-08-24 }}</ref>

== 参展与票房 ==

作为2002年第9届[[北京大学生电影节|北京大学生电影节]]参展影片，本片获得最佳导演处女作奖<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-cn | publisher = 网易 | title = 第九届北京大学生电影节获奖名单 | url = http://v.163.com/10/0211/15/5V8HTMT6008545QT.html | author =  | date =  | accessdate = 2010-07-14 | archive-date = 2019-05-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190520023447/http://v.163.com/10/0211/15/5V8HTMT6008545QT.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。此外，本片获选参与第59届[[威尼斯电影节|威尼斯电影节]]逆流而上非竞赛单元奖的角逐，虽在媒体中反应不错，但并未获得任何奖项<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-cn | publisher = 北京青年报 | title = 陆川威尼斯见闻：《寻枪》反响不错 | url = http://ent.163.com/edit/020906/020906_132979.html | author =  | date =  | accessdate = 2010-07-14 | archive-date = 2006-10-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20061016072020/http://ent.163.com/edit/020906/020906_132979.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | language = zh-cn | publisher = 南方都市报 | title = 《寻枪》首映 姜文缺席陆川独美 | url = http://ent.163.com/edit/020905/020905_132943.html | author =  | date =  | accessdate = 2010-07-14 | archive-date = 2016-03-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305024844/http://ent.163.com/edit/020905/020905_132943.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

影片自2002年5月9日在[[北京|北京]]首映以来，一周内即取得超过一百万票房，超过同期上映的好莱坞影片《[[护戒使者|指环王：护戒使者]]》<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-cn | publisher = 北京娱乐信报 | title = 《寻枪》击败《指环王》 全国票房超百万 | url = http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/c/2002-05-14/83127.html | author =  | date =  | accessdate = 2010-07-14 | archive-date = 2019-05-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190520133705/http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/c/2002-05-14/83127.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>，而中国总票房约700万元。
== 反响与评价 ==
=== 肯定 ===
本片作为[[陆川_(导演)|陆川]]导演和编剧的处女作，获得不少好评。有评论认为其为中国电影开创了一种新的模式，《[[南方周末|南方周末]]》甚至评论说，它“结束了电影在中国被神秘化的历史”，开创了“平民电影的新时代”<ref name="nfzm">{{cite web | language = zh-cn | publisher = 南方周末 | title = 新好电影：《寻枪》 | url = http://ent.163.com/edit/020510/020510_120169.html | author =  | date =  | accessdate = 2010-07-14 | archive-date = 2016-03-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305023948/http://ent.163.com/edit/020510/020510_120169.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | language = zh-cn | publisher = 京华时报 | title = 激情奔驰在旷野--《寻枪》为国产电影壮行 | url = http://ent.sina.com.cn/r/m/2002-05-13/82980.html | author =  | date = 2002年5月13日 | accessdate = 2010-07-14 | archive-date = 2019-05-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190520075817/http://ent.sina.com.cn/r/m/2002-05-13/82980.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。此外，本片亦是中国首部以数字方式放映的电影<ref name="digital cinema">{{cite web | language = zh-cn | publisher = 羊城晚报 | title = 上海启动全国首家数码影院 数码电影《寻枪》首映 | url = http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/c/2002-05-03/82062.html | author =  | date =  | accessdate = 2010-07-14 | archive-date = 2019-05-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190520045659/http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/c/2002-05-03/82062.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

=== 批评 ===
也有评论指出影片过分运用电影技巧，却忽视了剧本平庸的先天不足，同时借助媒体炒作票房、明星以及海外销售成绩，引起观众反感<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-cn | publisher = 武汉晨报 | title = 《寻枪》内容大于形式？ | url = http://www.southcn.com/ent/yulebest/200206030283.htm | author =  | date =  | accessdate = 2010-07-14 | archive-date = 2006-02-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20060218023901/http://www.southcn.com/ent/yulebest/200206030283.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。还有声音指责本片有抄袭日本导演[[黑泽明|黑泽明]]的名作《[[野良犬_(1949年電影)|野良犬]]》的嫌疑<ref name="yangcheng"/>。因本片对白采用贵州方言，[[国家语言文字工作委员会|国家语言文字工作委员会]]批评称此举有负面的示范效应，将影响[[推广普通话|推广普通话]]工作的开展<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-cn | publisher = 成都日报 | title = 语言文字工作委员会负责人批评姜文用方言拍电影 | url = http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/c/2002-09-02/090498453.html | author =  | date =  | accessdate = 2010-07-14 | archive-date = 2019-05-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190519102002/http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/c/2002-09-02/090498453.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。然而根据《[[中华人民共和国国家通用语言文字法|中华人民共和国国家通用语言文字法]]》的规定，戏曲、影视等艺术形式根据需要，可以使用方言。
